sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant CLI as ServiceConfigure
    participant Manager as ServiceManager

    User->>CLI: service:configure redis --set port=6380
    CLI->>CLI: parse set options
    CLI->>Manager: configure(service, config)
    Manager-->>CLI: success or error
    alt success
        CLI->>Manager: regenerateCompose
        CLI-->>User: configuration summary
    else error
        CLI-->>User: error message
    end
